        "content": "## ‚ö†Ô∏è NON-COMPLIANT PATH\n\n**Purpose:** Marks issues that don't meet release criteria.\n\n**Data Set:**\n- Issue Key\n- Reason: \"Definition of Done not met\"\n- Status: Non-Compliant\n\n**Next:** Creates tracking item in Monday.com"
