        "height": 364.8309178743961,
        "content": "## üìä PROJECT TRACKING\n\n**Purpose:** Creates a tracking item in Monday.com for non-compliant issues.\n\n**Board:** Release Issues\n**Group:** Topics\n\n**Item Details:**\n- Title: Non-Compliant: [Issue Key]\n- Reason for non-compliance\n- Current status\n\n**Benefit:** Centralized tracking of blockers"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
    },
    {
