      "name": "Sticky Note7",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "position": [
        336,
        1072
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "width": 543,
        "height": 306,
        "content": "## üéØ WORKFLOW SUMMARY\n\n**What This Automation Does:**\n\n1. **Monitors** Jira issues for updates\n2. **Validates** Definition of Done criteria\n3. **Separates** compliant from non-compliant issues\n4. **Tracks** blockers in Monday.com\n5. **Notifies** team via Slack\n\n**Use Case:** Ensures only release-ready issues make it to production\n\n**Team:** Release Management"
      },
      "typeVersion": 1
